\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {3.19}{\ignorespaces A plot of the width of an S2 versus the drift time for 32 keV events from \mhchem@ce@xiii {\noexpand ^{\noexpand 8\noexpand 3\noexpand m}\noexpand K\noexpand r}. Note that at a certain drift time, no more events are seen. This cut-off in events represents the location of the cathode since interactions below it will not produce an S2.}}{84}{figure.3.19}
